{
	"schemaVersion": 1,
	"id": "hexical",
	"version": "${version}",
	"name": "Hexical (Fixed for Connector)",
	"description": "【修复版】支持 HexCasting 0.11.3 + Sinytra Connector + Oculus\n\nOriginal: A fun addon containing genie lamps, mage blocks, specks, world scrying, and more!\n\n【已修复的问题】\n- ✅ OpReadMixin @Redirect 注入失败（HexCasting 0.11.3 兼容）\n- ✅ RenderLayer 循环初始化崩溃（Sinytra Connector 兼容）\n- ✅ Oculus Mixin 冲突（RenderType 静态初始化问题）\n\n【安装要求】\n- Minecraft 1.20.1\n- HexCasting 0.11.3\n- Sinytra Connector 1.0.0-beta.48+\n- Forge 47.4.16+\n\n【原始项目】https://github.com/miyucomics/hexical\n【修复版本】https://github.com/KJH50/hexical-fixed",
	"authors": [
		"miyucomics"
	],
	"contact": {
		"homepage": "https://miyucomics.github.io/hexical",
		"sources": "https://github.com/miyucomics/hexical"
	},
	"license": "MIT",
	"icon": "assets/hexical/icon.png",
	"environment": "*",
	"entrypoints": {
		"fabric-datagen": [
			{
				"adapter": "kotlin",
				"value": "miyucomics.hexical.datagen.HexicalDatagen"
			}
		],
		"main": [
			{
				"adapter": "kotlin",
				"value": "miyucomics.hexical.HexicalMain"
			}
		],
		"client": [
			{
				"adapter": "kotlin",
				"value": "miyucomics.hexical.HexicalClient"
			}
		],
		"cardinal-components": [
			"miyucomics.hexical.inits.HexicalCardinalComponents"
		],
		"emi": [
			"miyucomics.hexical.features.emi.HexicalEmi"
		]
	},
	"accessWidener" : "hexical.accesswidener",
	"mixins": [
		{
			"config": "hexical.client.mixins.json",
			"environment": "client"
		},
		"hexical.mixins.json"
	],
	"depends": {
		"minecraft": "1.20.1",
		"fabricloader": ">=0.16.7",
		"fabric-api": "*",
		"fabric-language-kotlin": ">=1.10.10+kotlin.1.9.10",
		"hexcasting": ">=0.11.1-7-pre-646",
		"hexpose": ">=1.0.0"
	},
	"custom": {
		"cardinal-components": [
			"hexical:muted"
		]
	}
}